# BucketBook Support

Need help? Email us at **support@bucket-book.com**

---

## Getting Started

**How do I track a game?**
Tap "New Game" from the home screen, select a player, enter the opponent name, and start logging stats by tapping the court or stat buttons.

**How do I add a player?**
Tap "Add Player" on the home screen and enter their name and jersey number.

## Account & Data

**How do I sync my data across devices?**
Sign in with your email or Apple ID. Your data will automatically sync to any device where you're signed in.

**How do I reset my password?**
On the sign-in screen, enter your email and tap "Forgot password?" to receive a reset link.

**How do I delete my account?**
Go to Menu → Account Settings → Delete Account. This permanently removes all your data.

## Subscriptions

**How do I manage my subscription?**
Subscriptions are managed through your Apple ID. Go to Settings → Your Name → Subscriptions on your device.

**How do I restore my purchase?**
Open the app, go to the upgrade screen, and tap "Restore Purchases."
